sellerCard.oneLiner: Front end web developer and HTML,WordPress website fixer
sellerCard.description: Hi I'm Shumaiz, a passionate front-end web developer with expertise in WordPress development and website issue resolution. Whether you need a stunning website design, seamless functionality, or troubleshooting for pesky problems, I’m here to help! With a keen eye for detail and a commitment to delivering high-quality results, I ensure your online presence shines. Let’s bring your vision to life!

description.content:
"DO NOT PLACE ORDER DIRECTLY BEFORE DISCUSSION"


Before start the order !

Please Text ME to discuss the project details.


Hi.I am professional Senior Front End developer specialist since 2018, In my professional career i have done many projects with different techniques, i have strong grip on Html css3 Bootstrap, media-queries, Jquery and javascript.


If you want to convert your PSD, XD, AI, Sketch, PNG or JPG  file into responsive website you are at right place and we can discuss the work and proceed.


Following are some of my core skills


  1. HTML5
  2. CSS3
  3. Bootstrap
  4. JQuery
  5. Responsive template
  6. Cross-browser compatibility
  7. Pixel perfect design
  8. Clean code
  9. Integrate custom fonts
  10. W3C validated


This is not the exhaustive list of what I can do. Please discuss with me your custom requirements and I will try my best to assist you. Thanks

questionsAndAnswers.question: How to start the order ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Send me your requirements in inbox i'll check them and we'll discuss budget and timeline and after we finalize i will send you a custom offer.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you do backend as well ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No i will do only front end web development.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How much you'll charge and timeline for one landing page ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Starting price for one landing page is 25$ which will have 3-4 sections and i will check the complexity of the design's, if we have complex project's price may increase and timeline for one simple landing page is one day.

reviews.comment: What an amazing service, professionalism and fast. Very respectful and patient too. Many people didn’t know how to fix the issue for weeks. But shumaiz did it in hours.

The work was absolutely outstanding! They exceeded all expectations, delivering a flawless website with speed, precision, and creativity. Their attention to detail, problem-solving skills, and dedication were truly exceptional. Communication was seamless, and they went above and beyond to ensure perfection. Highly recommend for any web development project!

This is the second time I've used Shumaize for a Wordpress project. When I give up trying to figure out how to do something tricky in Wordpress, I know it's time to turn to him. He is great to work with. Very professional, quick to respond, and delivered on the task as agreed on.
The freelancer quickly identified and fixed a critical error on my WordPress site . Fast, professional, and knowledgeable—I highly recommend them for any WordPress issues!
